laura.whitaker-wallace.foster.body: Hi Wallace. This is your daily check-in. How are you doing today?
hi. im ok. just a little tired
I'm sorry to hear that. I hope you feel better soon.
I'm here if you need anything. Have you registered for single parent classes yet?
no. i dont think i can afford it
I understand. I'll send you some information about financial aid.
hi did you send that information yet?
I'm sorry, I haven't had a chance to yet. I'll send it to you now.
this is not helpful. i dont qualify for any of these. im very disappointed. i wish you offered better financial aid

winston.ledford-dianne.shaw.body: Afternoon. Did you receive my financial aid application?
Yes, I did. I'm sorry, but you don't qualify for any of our financial aid programs
That's disappointing. Do you offer any other classes for single parents?
Yes! We also have a number of classes that are free, including a free online parenting class. I'll send you some more information shortly
Did you receive the flyer I just sent?
Yes! This is exactly what I'm looking for. Thank you!

asuka-ito-hideyoshi-sato.body: Hi Hide! I just wanted to let you know that I'll be out of the office tomorrow, and Dianne will check in with you instead. Let me know if you need anything else!
but why. i want to talk to you not a stranger
I understand. Dianne is a fantastic person to talk to and I promise you'll enjoy talking with her for anything you may need
ugh no. i guess ill just wait till your back. i dont want to talk to anyone else
i hate this organization. not helpful at all. you especially are always absent when i need you most
I'm sorry you feel that way. I'll be back in the office on Wednesday and we can talk then. I hope you have a great day!
